        "content": "```\nPortfolio drawdown thresholds:\n\nNORMAL  (< -10%):  Full trading, full position sizes\nSOFT    (-10%):    Position sizes halved (size_multiplier = 0.5)\nHARD    (-20%):    No new trades opened, defensive sells allowed\nKILL    (-30%):    ALL positions force-liquidated, trading halted\n\nCooldown: 24 hours after breaker trips before reassessment\n```\n\n### What happens at each level:\n\n**SOFT (-10% drawdown)**\n- Cancel aggressive signals\n- Halve Kelly position sizes\n- Continue trading but more conservatively\n- \"Yellow light\"\n\n**HARD (-20% drawdown)**\n- Cancel all pending BUY signals\n- Allow SELL signals (to reduce exposure)\n- No new positions opened\n- \"Red light\"\n\n**KILL (-30% drawdown)**\n- Cancel ALL pending signals\n- **Force-liquidate all open positions** (Session 9 safety fix)\n- Create SELL trades at current market price\n- Halt trading completely\n- \"Emergency stop\""
